*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]] /'O:g@st/

===Proper Noun===
'''August''' (''plural:'' '''[[Augusts]]''')

# the eighth [[month]] of the year, after [[July]] and before [[September]], in the [[Julian]] and [[Gregorian calendar]]s, having 31 [[day]]s.
#: ''Hot August night.''
# male proper name.
#: ''August Derleth was a science fiction author.''

*''Month of the year:'' '''August'''
**'''Last:''' [[July]]
**'''Next:''' [[September]]

